properties.text:
[color=#ffff00]Bowling rules:[/color] Knock down the pins with the ball. Each game has 10 frames, with up to 2 rolls to knock the 10 pins.

[color=#ffff00]Scoring:[/color]
- Strike (knock all pins in the 1st roll): 10 + next 2 rolls.
- Spare (knock all pins in 2 rolls): 10 + next roll.
- Open Frame: total pins knocked down in the frame.

[color=#ffff00]10th Frame:[/color] Get extra rolls by a spare or strike.

[color=#ffff00]Controls:[/color] ARROWS to move & SPACE to aim, charge and roll.

Press [color=#ffff00]SPACE[/color] to start...
